*** ../vim-7.4.054/src/config.h.in	2013-02-26 14:18:19.000000000 +0100
--- src/config.h.in	2013-11-02 20:52:08.000000000 +0100
***************
*** 442,444 ****
--- 442,447 ----
  
  /* Define if you want Cygwin to use the WIN32 clipboard, not compatible with X11*/
